data.description: Walk in and enjoy a welcoming entrance which opens to a bright and open floor plan that includes a main floor great room, large kitchen and dining plus a main floor bedroom w/ closet and full bath that can also be used as an office or flex space. A step away from the kitchen is access to the large garage with enough room for extra storage. Lots of windows fill the upstairs with natural light where you'll find loft area, the owner's suite w/ walk-in closet and full bath plus two more nicely sized bedrooms, laundry and another full bathroom. Outside is a large flat yard for entertaining backed by mature trees. Close to downtown Burlington, shopping and major highways. Freshly painted! Shed, refrigerator, washer & dryer convey!
